## §1. BUTTERFLY EFFECT — GIAI VE THU 2

### §1.1 Ve thu 1 (TIME axis — em da spec trong SPEC_RADIATION_UNIVERSAL_v1.0)

```
Stress_total(n, t) = ∫₀ᵗ [Stress_X(τ) + R_time(τ)] dτ
Cell chet khi: Stress_total > Capacity(n, t) = n × e^(-γ₀(n+1)t)
```

**Co che:** small input × infinite time = catastrophe. Catch bang thoai-sinh co chu ky.

### §1.2 Ve thu 2 (RESONANCE axis — QIINT2 co che)

```
T(Z_E, Z_C) = exp(-((Z_E - Z_C) / σ_u)² / 2)
Outcome:
  T > 0.75  →  FALL (cell match, tao TouchRecord)
  T < 0.20  →  DISSIPATE (tan trong field)
  0.20 ≤ T ≤ 0.75  →  OSCILLATE (loop → ISEU mark suspicious)
```

**Co che:** small frequency match × impedance overlap = cascade into cell. Catch bang Z₀ baseline + transmission bell curve.

### §1.3 Butterfly effect INTEGRATED

**2 ve hop nhat trong survival-cell:**

| axis | mechanism | catch |
|---|---|---|
| TIME | Stress_total accumulate | thoai-sinh at t_critical |
| RESONANCE | Z_E vs Z_C match | filter at Z₀ gate |

**Survival-cell = gate cho CA 2 axis truoc khi signal vao field semantic.**

