## §2. SURVIVAL-CELL Z₀ BASELINE

Per SPEC_QIINT_PHYSICS_FOUNDATION §5.1 cell baseline pattern:

| Cell | Z₀ | Role |
|------|-----|------|
| quantum-defense | 0.5 | strict nhat (filter nhieu) |
| gatekeeper | 0.8 | enforce policy |
| khai-cell | 1.0 | sensor neutral |
| finance-cell | 1.1 | conservative |
| sales-cell | 1.2 | permissive |
| **survival-cell** | **0.3** | **THAP NHAT — gate TRUOC tat ca** |

**Rationale Z₀ = 0.3:**
- Tang 0 phai catch signal TRUOC khi vao tang 1-4
- Z₀ thap = chi accept signal co Z_E gan 0.3 (resource-friendly)
- Signal co Z_E > 0.3 (resource-heavy) → reflect (R > 0) → NOT accepted
- Parameter σ_u = ln(2) (DRAFT per §5.3, pending calibration P1-03)

